# Breakout Game

## Overview

This is a simple 2D Breakout game built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. The game includes a paddle, a ball, and bricks that the player must break to score points.

## Features

- Paddle controlled by arrow keys
- Breakable bricks
- Score tracking
- Lives counter
- Game over and win conditions

## Getting Started

### Prerequisites

- Web browser (e.g., Chrome, Firefox, Safari)

### Installation

1. Clone the repository:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/your-username/breakout-game.git
   ```
